<section class="section prp-h-s8">
  <div class="container container--narrow">

    <h2 class="prp-h-s8__heading">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="prp-h-s8__faq-item">
      <h3 class="prp-h-s8__faq-question">What Is PRP Hair Restoration?</h3>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">Platelet-Rich Plasma for Hair (PRP) is an innovative treatment derived from a small sample of your own blood. After collection, your blood is processed in a centrifuge to concentrate the platelets, which contain powerful growth factors essential for tissue regeneration and healing.</p>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">At Menon Medispa, under the direction of regenerative medicine specialist Dr. Aditi Menon, we precisely inject this concentrated PRP solution into targeted areas of your scalp, awakening dormant hair follicles and stimulating the natural growth cycle.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prp-h-s8__faq-item">
      <h3 class="prp-h-s8__faq-question">Am I a Good Candidate for PRP Hair Restoration?</h3>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">Most people experiencing hair thinning or loss are excellent candidates for PRP treatments. These procedures are particularly effective for:</p>
      <ul class="prp-h-s8__list">
        <li>Early to moderate stages of pattern baldness</li>
        <li>Stress-related hair thinning</li>
        <li>Postpartum hair loss</li>
        <li>Age-related hair thinning</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">Ideal candidates are in good overall health without blood clotting disorders or certain autoimmune conditions. A thorough consultation will help determine your suitability.</p>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">We recommend scheduling a consultation with Dr. Menon to determine your specific condition and goals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prp-h-s8__faq-item">
      <h3 class="prp-h-s8__faq-question">What Results Can I Expect?</h3>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">Following PRP hair restoration treatments, you can typically expect:</p>
      <ul class="prp-h-s8__list">
        <li>Reduced hair shedding within 2-3 weeks</li>
        <li>Increased hair thickness and strength over 2-3 months</li>
        <li>Improved hair growth in previously thinning areas after 4-6 months</li>
        <li>Enhanced overall hair quality and resilience</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="prp-h-s8__faq-body">For optimal results, we generally recommend a series of 3 treatments spaced 4-6 weeks apart, followed by maintenance sessions every 6-12 months.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

